public class GreenesRTree
extends RTree

An RTree implementing the split-strategy proposed by D. Greene. For a detailed discussion see D. Greene: "An Implementation and Performance Analysis of Spatial Data Access Methods", Proc. 5th Int. Conf. on Data Engineering, 606-615, 1989.
